  "category": "Phase 1: Production-Grade Foundation",
  "description": "**Milestone:** Phase 1: Production-Grade Foundation\n\nCreate Astro Starlight documentation pages for all 13 components with: overview, API reference (from CEM), usage examples, accessibility guide, Drupal integration, theming guide, and extension guide.\n\n**Files to Modify:**\n- apps/docs/src/content/docs/components/\n\n**Acceptance Criteria:**\n- [ ] Every component has a dedicated Starlight page\n- [ ] API reference auto-generated from CEM data\n- [ ] Usage examples with code snippets\n- [ ] Accessibility section with ARIA patterns and keyboard shortcuts\n- [ ] Drupal integration section with Twig template examples\n- [ ] Theming section showing token override patterns\n\n**Complexity:** large",
